1
00:00:49,151 --> 00:00:50,085
Talay...

2
00:00:50,433 --> 00:00:52,102
do you know the person in this picture?

3
00:00:54,183 --> 00:00:56,252
Tao Sor has no need for these memories.

4
00:00:56,566 --> 00:01:01,170
You think by doing this, Tao Sor will truly be happy?

5
00:01:01,438 --> 00:01:04,274
We must clear out anything that can destroy his life.

6
00:01:04,808 --> 00:01:06,677
If you really feel bad,

7
00:01:06,843 --> 00:01:08,211
then I beg you.

8
00:01:08,912 --> 00:01:11,248
Quit messing with that family's son!

9
00:01:11,548 --> 00:01:12,916
Your name is Tao Sor.

10
00:01:14,384 --> 00:01:18,188
We're at The Precious Resort, with Mom and Dad.

11
00:01:20,757 --> 00:01:21,825
Why...

12
00:01:23,560 --> 00:01:25,529
can't I remember anything?

13
00:01:28,632 --> 00:01:29,433
It's okay.

14
00:01:30,434 --> 00:01:32,569
I'll be jogging your memory every morning.

15
00:01:32,769 --> 00:01:36,406
About the people who've had direct experience,

16
00:01:36,673 --> 00:01:38,442
would there be anyone still alive?

17
00:01:49,753 --> 00:01:50,988
I know you, right?

18
00:01:51,822 --> 00:01:54,825
And we also have memories together...

19
00:01:56,927 --> 00:01:57,561
right?

20
00:01:58,729 --> 00:01:59,429
Yes!

21
00:02:01,865 --> 00:02:03,200
We love each other very much.

22
00:02:04,067 --> 00:02:05,769
We really love each other.

23
00:02:09,272 --> 00:02:11,808
And..why don't you...

24
00:02:13,477 --> 00:02:15,012
ever come to see me?

25
00:02:16,880 --> 00:02:18,281
Why did you...

26
00:02:20,117 --> 00:02:21,985
leave me in the dark like this..

27
00:02:24,788 --> 00:02:26,023
did I do something wrong?

28
00:02:26,590 --> 00:02:27,224
Not at all!

29
00:02:28,625 --> 00:02:29,993
You didn't do anything wrong, Tao Sor.

30
00:02:31,228 --> 00:02:32,062
I'm sorry.

31
00:02:32,763 --> 00:02:34,998
But from now, I won't ever leave you.

32
00:02:35,766 --> 00:02:38,468
I'll be here as your memory,

33
00:02:39,770 --> 00:02:40,570
your boyfriend,

34
00:02:41,638 --> 00:02:44,041
and everything else for you.

35
00:02:49,713 --> 00:02:51,882
And how will I know that you'll keep your word?

36
00:02:54,317 --> 00:02:55,285
Tomorrow...

37
00:02:57,721 --> 00:02:58,989
I wake up...

38
00:02:59,890 --> 00:03:01,224
and I'll just forget everything.

39
00:03:02,826 --> 00:03:04,061
But this...

40
00:03:08,865 --> 00:03:10,867
will never fade away.

41
00:05:18,695 --> 00:05:19,663
Talay.

42
00:05:21,998 --> 00:05:23,466
What do you have to hide from me?

43
00:05:25,335 --> 00:05:26,536
About if I remember anything?

44
00:05:40,806 --> 00:05:42,708
Becuase Kim's hurt several times already!

45
00:05:43,008 --> 00:05:43,842
Not at all.

46
00:05:45,244 --> 00:05:46,278
He didn't hurt me.

47
00:05:47,246 --> 00:05:48,447
I love him.

48
00:05:49,815 --> 00:05:50,649
He just...

49
00:05:52,084 --> 00:05:53,619
wants me to have memories of every day.

50
00:05:54,219 --> 00:05:55,821
I remind you every day as well!

51
00:05:57,556 --> 00:05:58,857
That you're my younger brother,

52
00:05:59,958 --> 00:06:01,226
that you're a son to your parents,

53
00:06:02,494 --> 00:06:03,962
so why do you have to listen to him?

54
00:06:04,496 --> 00:06:05,564
Why are you angry at me?

55
00:06:10,502 --> 00:06:12,004
You afraid I'll remember something?

56
00:06:19,077 --> 00:06:19,845
Alright.

57
00:06:20,813 --> 00:06:21,547
If you won't tell me,

58
00:06:22,281 --> 00:06:23,148
I'll go ask Mom.

59
00:06:23,582 --> 00:06:24,383
Don't.

60
00:06:25,017 --> 00:06:25,784
I beg you.

61
00:06:26,852 --> 00:06:27,853
Don't ask Mom yet.

62
00:06:28,787 --> 00:06:29,455
Fine.

63
00:06:33,926 --> 00:06:36,795
If you want me to feel like I still love you,

64
00:06:37,529 --> 00:06:38,597
can you please explain?

65
00:06:40,065 --> 00:06:40,899
I really don't know.

66
00:06:41,567 --> 00:06:42,935
It could be something before...

67
00:06:43,368 --> 00:06:44,937
I even met you.

68
00:06:45,737 --> 00:06:46,538
Met me?

69
00:06:49,741 --> 00:06:50,876
What do you mean?

70
00:06:52,444 --> 00:06:54,079
16 years ago...

71
00:06:55,380 --> 00:06:56,815
I found you...

72
00:06:58,050 --> 00:06:59,885
washed up on the beach.

73
00:07:10,596 --> 00:07:12,264
Hey, hey!

74
00:07:12,264 --> 00:07:13,398
Can you hear me?

75
00:07:13,732 --> 00:07:14,466
Wake up!

76
00:07:15,400 --> 00:07:16,268
Kid!

77
00:07:20,439 --> 00:07:23,442
Kid, can you hear me? I'm gonna try to help you.

78
00:07:32,718 --> 00:07:33,285
Kid!

79
00:07:34,219 --> 00:07:35,220
Stay calm, okay?

80
00:07:42,581 --> 00:07:44,049
It fits you perfectly.

81
00:07:45,283 --> 00:07:47,252
Hungry? Eat something first.

82
00:07:48,587 --> 00:07:50,122
Can I have that?

83
00:07:51,390 --> 00:07:52,991
You have the same taste as my brother.

84
00:07:54,626 --> 00:07:57,129
My name's Talay, what's your name?

85
00:07:58,063 --> 00:07:59,498
I...

86
00:08:02,768 --> 00:08:04,736
don't know.

87
00:08:07,572 --> 00:08:09,474
It's okay, take your time to think.

88
00:08:09,875 --> 00:08:13,578
Do you remember where you came from, and how you ended up on the beach?

89
00:08:15,947 --> 00:08:16,782
It's okay.

90
00:08:18,683 --> 00:08:19,551
Tao Sor!

91
00:08:20,018 --> 00:08:20,852
Tao Sor!

92
00:08:21,253 --> 00:08:22,087
Tao Sor!

93
00:08:22,087 --> 00:08:23,688
Tao Sor! Where have you been, son?

94
00:08:23,688 --> 00:08:25,390
I missed you so much!

95
00:08:25,524 --> 00:08:28,627
Don't ever disappear like that, stay with Mom, okay?

96
00:08:36,635 --> 00:08:37,702
Mom?

97
00:08:41,106 --> 00:08:42,574
This isn't him.

98
00:08:42,808 --> 00:08:45,210
I found him washed up on the beach.

99
00:08:47,712 --> 00:08:48,914
Oh...

100
00:08:50,982 --> 00:08:52,017
Are you tired?

101
00:08:53,251 --> 00:08:55,220
Get some food inside you first, okay?

102
00:09:02,928 --> 00:09:04,896
Tomorrow, I'll take you to the police

103
00:09:05,130 --> 00:09:07,666
and we'll find your parents, okay?

104
00:09:31,857 --> 00:09:33,225
Hey, kid!

105
00:09:34,092 --> 00:09:34,926
Kid!

106
00:09:36,428 --> 00:09:37,529
What's the matter?

107
00:09:38,296 --> 00:09:39,130
Kid!

108
00:09:39,564 --> 00:09:41,566
Kid! Is something wrong?

109
00:09:44,503 --> 00:09:45,337
Kid!

110
00:09:54,012 --> 00:09:56,414
Who are you? And where am I?

111
00:09:58,083 --> 00:10:00,619
Don't you remember? It's me, Talay.

112
00:10:01,987 --> 00:10:03,221
What is this place?

113
00:10:06,258 --> 00:10:08,994
Don't be scared, I'll take care of you.

114
00:10:12,364 --> 00:10:13,865
Tao Sor!

115
00:10:15,433 --> 00:10:18,103
Everything's okay, son. Your mom's here.

116
00:10:18,770 --> 00:10:20,405
My name's Tao Sor?
- Yes.

117
00:10:20,705 --> 00:10:23,708
You're my son, okay? Stay with mommy.

118
00:10:26,111 --> 00:10:27,145
After that,

119
00:10:27,445 --> 00:10:29,848
we tried to find your parents,

120
00:10:30,282 --> 00:10:32,083
but no one ever showed up.

121
00:11:15,627 --> 00:11:18,630
Hello, Tao Sor. My name is Talay.

122
00:11:18,730 --> 00:11:20,432
I am your older brother.

123
00:11:20,732 --> 00:11:22,133
My name's Tao Sor?

124
00:12:16,855 --> 00:12:19,991
That's right. You are my younger brother.

125
00:12:20,492 --> 00:12:23,495
We live with our parents here, at this resort.

126
00:12:34,572 --> 00:12:35,974
That means...

127
00:12:38,643 --> 00:12:40,145
I'm not really Mom and Da's son, right?

128
00:12:40,311 --> 00:12:41,146
That's not it!

129
00:12:42,647 --> 00:12:43,982
You are my brother,

130
00:12:44,616 --> 00:12:45,950
you are Mom and Dad's son,

131
00:12:48,253 --> 00:12:51,256
you are really a member of our family.

132
00:12:56,695 --> 00:12:57,662
Tao Sor...

133
00:13:00,065 --> 00:13:00,832
Listen to me.

134
00:13:03,368 --> 00:13:04,502
Tao Sor, wait!

135
00:13:05,704 --> 00:13:07,338
Tao Sor!

136
00:14:23,815 --> 00:14:24,482
Tao Sor!

137
00:14:29,187 --> 00:14:30,188
What are you doing?

138
00:14:31,289 --> 00:14:32,891
I am not Tao Sor.

139
00:14:35,493 --> 00:14:36,895
I don't know who I am.

140
00:14:39,898 --> 00:14:41,232
They just took me in...

141
00:14:46,905 --> 00:14:47,705
I don't know...

142
00:14:49,974 --> 00:14:51,342
why I'm even alive.

143
00:14:57,816 --> 00:14:59,684
You're alive so we can love each other.

144
00:15:10,528 --> 00:15:12,630
I don't want to remember anymore.

145
00:15:22,574 --> 00:15:23,775
You're sure about that?

146
00:15:24,576 --> 00:15:25,510
Since you said that...

147
00:15:28,980 --> 00:15:30,448
Because if you need that,

148
00:15:32,083 --> 00:15:33,284
starting tomorrow,

149
00:15:34,853 --> 00:15:36,221
I won't come see you anymore.

150
00:15:38,690 --> 00:15:40,425
You could go back to your old life,

151
00:15:41,593 --> 00:15:42,827
and be Tao Sor as always.

152
00:15:44,562 --> 00:15:45,296
No...

153
00:15:46,297 --> 00:15:47,899
I still want to see you.

154
00:15:49,500 --> 00:15:50,969
Don't leave me like the others.

155
00:15:59,043 --> 00:16:00,578
If that's what you need,

156
00:16:02,413 --> 00:16:04,349
I will be your memory for you.

157
00:16:05,350 --> 00:16:09,454
And no matter how beautiful or hurtful that memory is,

158
00:16:10,121 --> 00:16:11,122
I promise...

159
00:16:12,257 --> 00:16:13,892
that I will always be by your side.

160
00:16:39,951 --> 00:16:40,752
Get over here.

161
00:16:41,886 --> 00:16:43,121
Are you really my friend?

162
00:16:43,655 --> 00:16:44,255
Huh?!
Of course I am!

163
00:16:46,024 --> 00:16:47,258
I've known you for years,

164
00:16:48,126 --> 00:16:50,161
So why the fuck are you helping Kim?!

165
00:16:51,162 --> 00:16:51,763
Talay...

166
00:16:52,864 --> 00:16:54,232
I wasn't helping Kim,

167
00:16:55,099 --> 00:16:56,100
it was for Tao Sor.

168
00:16:58,136 --> 00:16:59,504
I really love you, man.

169
00:17:00,872 --> 00:17:01,472
But I also

170
00:17:02,006 --> 00:17:02,941
love Tao Sor.

171
00:17:06,177 --> 00:17:07,712
The reason I did this, is because...

172
00:17:08,379 --> 00:17:10,381
I can't keep seeing Tao Sor get hurt again.

173
00:17:11,149 --> 00:17:12,617
So you're saying...

174
00:17:13,785 --> 00:17:15,954
I hurt Tao Sor, is that it?

175
00:17:18,122 --> 00:17:18,890
Daiji...

176
00:17:20,325 --> 00:17:22,593
you will never understand how I feel.

177
00:17:23,328 --> 00:17:25,530
I've been looking after Tao Sor for years,

178
00:17:26,264 --> 00:17:27,732
I took good care of him,

179
00:17:28,733 --> 00:17:29,701
Bu today...

180
00:17:30,535 --> 00:17:32,503
you ruined everything!

181
00:17:33,338 --> 00:17:34,672
The one who destroyed everything,

182
00:17:34,772 --> 00:17:35,573
isn't me...

183
00:17:36,474 --> 00:17:37,508
but you!

184
00:17:42,513 --> 00:17:44,248
From now on, you and I are no longer friends!

185
00:17:46,351 --> 00:17:48,019
What are you guys fighting about?

186
00:17:50,054 --> 00:17:51,322
Whatever works for you, then.

187
00:17:51,923 --> 00:17:52,657
Daiji!

188
00:17:52,924 --> 00:17:54,058
Get back to work,

189
00:17:54,292 --> 00:17:55,493
I'll talk to him.

190
00:18:11,109 --> 00:18:12,110
Let go!

191
00:18:12,777 --> 00:18:14,946
Let me go!
- Stop and calm down first.

192
00:18:15,613 --> 00:18:16,447
I said "Let go"

193
00:18:17,048 --> 00:18:17,782
Let go!

194
00:18:18,149 --> 00:18:18,983
I won't let go,

195
00:18:19,183 --> 00:18:20,084
until you stop!

196
00:18:24,188 --> 00:18:25,023
Let go!

197
00:18:25,490 --> 00:18:26,124
Mor!

198
00:18:27,825 --> 00:18:29,093
Let me go!

199
00:18:32,430 --> 00:18:34,098
Tao Sor knows the truth about Kim.

200
00:18:34,932 --> 00:18:37,935
Daiji was the one showed Tao Sor those pictures.

201
00:18:44,742 --> 00:18:46,177
That's not all.

202
00:18:48,046 --> 00:18:51,682
Tao Sor now knows, that he's not my real brother!

203
00:18:56,487 --> 00:18:59,590
I have to do everything to make him forget,

204
00:19:00,258 --> 00:19:02,126
and come back to being the Tao Sor I know!

205
00:19:07,098 --> 00:19:08,533
Or is it finally time?

206
00:19:09,534 --> 00:19:10,968
That you have to let Tao Sor go?

207
00:19:11,269 --> 00:19:13,004
Are you even on my side?

208
00:19:13,404 --> 00:19:14,305
Huh?!

209
00:19:14,872 --> 00:19:15,873
I'm saying this...

210
00:19:16,607 --> 00:19:18,376
not because I'm worried about Tao Sor,

211
00:19:18,743 --> 00:19:20,211
but because I'm worried about you!

212
00:19:20,845 --> 00:19:23,081
How many more times are you gonna torture yourself with this?

213
00:19:23,214 --> 00:19:25,817
If you're not gonna help me, that's fine.

214
00:19:26,884 --> 00:19:29,420
But I'm not gonna lose Tao Sor again.

215
00:19:46,204 --> 00:19:48,139
Normally, what kind of things do you ask for?

216
00:19:48,906 --> 00:19:53,177
I ask for my ship to be safe, and to catch a lot of fish.

217
00:19:53,544 --> 00:19:56,547
And whenever you got out to sea, do you ever see typhoons?

218
00:19:56,714 --> 00:19:59,484
It's a normal thing for sailors.

219
00:20:00,051 --> 00:20:03,855
I see many typhoons, sometimes I don't even know

220
00:20:04,222 --> 00:20:07,225
if I'll survive or not, but usually I do.

221
00:20:07,625 --> 00:20:11,062
But I do think that the Holy Spirits are looking after me.

222
00:20:11,295 --> 00:20:14,532
And normally, do they have any signs or signals for typhoons?

223
00:20:15,500 --> 00:20:18,069
This many questions, will I go on TV?

224
00:20:18,569 --> 00:20:21,305
You won't, but you'll get merits.

225
00:20:23,107 --> 00:20:26,410
Then why am I even here? Wasting my work day.

226
00:20:26,611 --> 00:20:27,712
I got mouths to feed!

227
00:20:28,012 --> 00:20:31,015
What kind of interview is this? I'm outta here!

228
00:20:36,020 --> 00:20:38,289
Sometimes the people here are like that.

229
00:20:38,656 --> 00:20:41,259
That's okay, I've got someone lined up for an interview.

230
00:20:41,592 --> 00:20:42,793
This one's a Shero.

231
00:20:43,027 --> 00:20:43,694
Who?

232
00:20:44,061 --> 00:20:47,064
Remember the list of people you had me contact?

233
00:20:47,165 --> 00:20:50,301
I found one name, but she moved overseas.

234
00:20:50,535 --> 00:20:53,538
But she's in Thailand right now, so I contacted her for an interview.

235
00:21:00,578 --> 00:21:01,412
Which one?

236
00:21:02,813 --> 00:21:05,016
She said she'll be dressed in black.

237
00:21:23,434 --> 00:21:26,003
I've came to ask the Deities here before,

238
00:21:26,370 --> 00:21:31,609
to let me find my lost son, but my wishes have never came true.

239
00:21:32,410 --> 00:21:35,913
Can you tell us what the typhoon was like for you?

240
00:21:36,447 --> 00:21:40,885
That day, our family went out on a ship with Siam Sea.

241
00:21:41,385 --> 00:21:46,324
We were celebrating my boyfriend becoming a Chef.

242
00:21:46,457 --> 00:21:49,193
All of a sudden, the sky changed color.

243
00:21:49,393 --> 00:21:53,464
The typhoon came with no warning, with waves as tall as mountains.

244
00:21:53,531 --> 00:21:55,933
my son who had just turned 5 years old,

245
00:21:56,234 --> 00:21:57,668
was so suprised.

246
00:21:57,868 --> 00:22:02,273
There was a young man on the ship trying to help him,

247
00:22:02,273 --> 00:22:05,443
but the ship rocked over, throwing everyone overboard.

248
00:22:05,776 --> 00:22:08,112
I was holding onto Joe,

249
00:22:08,412 --> 00:22:12,617
but I fell in the water, and the current was too strong.

250
00:22:13,184 --> 00:22:16,187
And I have no idea when I fell in.

251
00:22:16,387 --> 00:22:18,389
And after that, what happened?

252
00:22:19,056 --> 00:22:23,261
I thought I was dead, but I was able to wake up.

253
00:22:24,028 --> 00:22:27,565
Then I found out that I've been Sleeping Beauty for over 3 years.

254
00:22:27,865 --> 00:22:29,700
And your son and boyfriend?

255
00:22:30,101 --> 00:22:33,104
My husband lost his life at sea,

256
00:22:33,204 --> 00:22:37,775
as for my son, he was swallowed by the sea, disappearing without a trace.

257
00:22:39,944 --> 00:22:41,579
Enough?

258
00:22:46,083 --> 00:22:48,419
At first, I couldn't take it.

259
00:22:48,853 --> 00:22:50,454
I tried to find him,

260
00:22:50,821 --> 00:22:54,292
but the officers said it's already been 3 years.

261
00:22:54,592 --> 00:22:56,827
If they could, then they would have already found him.

262
00:23:10,741 --> 00:23:12,843
I couldn't accept it.

263
00:23:13,010 --> 00:23:15,546
Waking up and knowing that there was no one left.

264
00:23:15,780 --> 00:23:19,850
Both my husband and son, so I moved overseas.

265
00:23:30,461 --> 00:23:34,031
We are really sorry for you, and...

266
00:23:34,231 --> 00:23:37,435
me and Siam Sea will have to truly apologize for this tragic loss.

267
00:23:38,069 --> 00:23:40,304
My own family also...

268
00:23:40,471 --> 00:23:43,474
lost our brother from this incident.

269
00:23:43,874 --> 00:23:45,409
I was very young back then,

270
00:23:45,776 --> 00:23:47,745
and no one ever told me this story.

271
00:23:48,245 --> 00:23:50,448
But once I got to hear it from you,

272
00:23:51,015 --> 00:23:55,086
I realize how hurt everyone is.

273
00:23:55,653 --> 00:23:56,887
This should be enough, right?

274
00:24:00,024 --> 00:24:01,826
Thank you so much.

275
00:24:02,226 --> 00:24:05,496
I know that telling this story must be very hard for you.

276
00:24:05,896 --> 00:24:09,967
But I believe that this will benefit so many people.

277
00:24:10,768 --> 00:24:12,403
I also have to thank you.

278
00:24:12,870 --> 00:24:15,339
Being able to let this out has been good.

279
00:24:15,873 --> 00:24:17,508
Ever since I moved,

280
00:24:18,142 --> 00:24:21,145
I haven't told anyone this story.

281
00:24:21,779 --> 00:24:24,782
Then, we'll take you out to dinner.

282
00:24:25,082 --> 00:24:27,218
There's one really good place,

283
00:24:28,252 --> 00:24:30,554
take it as a local bringing you out on a trip!

284
00:24:31,522 --> 00:24:33,491
Shall we get going?

285
00:24:35,826 --> 00:24:38,329
You're so sweet.
- It's true.

286
00:24:45,503 --> 00:24:49,206
Your food is here! This is the chef's signature dish,

287
00:24:49,206 --> 00:24:50,741
please enjoy!

288
00:24:58,282 --> 00:25:01,285
Um, let's start eating.

289
00:25:27,044 --> 00:25:30,414
Delicious as always.
- True! It's so good, it's my favorite.

290
00:25:34,785 --> 00:25:37,388
Is something going on?

291
00:25:49,900 --> 00:25:51,268
Are you okay?

292
00:25:51,435 --> 00:25:54,004
The food doesn't fit you taste, right? I'll tell the chef right away!

293
00:25:59,143 --> 00:26:00,878
Tao Sor! We have a problem!

294
00:26:04,415 --> 00:26:06,684
I apologize, what's wrong with this dish?

295
00:26:43,320 --> 00:26:46,323
You're the one who made this dish?

296
00:26:47,191 --> 00:26:47,858
Yes.

297
00:26:48,325 --> 00:26:52,663
It reminded me of my late husband's cooking,

298
00:26:52,663 --> 00:26:54,031
thank you so much.

299
00:26:58,736 --> 00:27:00,504
It's...no problem.

300
00:27:01,872 --> 00:27:02,740
Tao Sor.

301
00:27:03,407 --> 00:27:04,275
Tao Sor.

302
00:27:05,476 --> 00:27:06,744
What happened, son?

303
00:27:09,313 --> 00:27:10,948
I'm sorry for startling everyone.

304
00:27:11,148 --> 00:27:15,986
The dish that Chef made, reminded me of my husband

305
00:27:15,986 --> 00:27:18,022
and son, who both passed away.

306
00:27:18,122 --> 00:27:19,590
My condolences.

307
00:27:19,590 --> 00:27:21,058
Thank you for the food.

308
00:27:21,325 --> 00:27:24,161
Your son is talented, and so sweet.

309
00:27:24,261 --> 00:27:27,264
If my son was still here, he'd probably be around this age.

310
00:27:27,798 --> 00:27:29,700
Please enjoy.

311
00:27:35,539 --> 00:27:38,976
Once we're free, we should find a place to go camping with the kids.

312
00:27:39,243 --> 00:27:42,479
So we can have activites together. Where should we go?
- Of course, honey!

313
00:27:42,746 --> 00:27:44,081
That looks nice.

314
00:27:44,682 --> 00:27:45,749
I think it's too far.

315
00:27:46,216 --> 00:27:48,152
We could go to Nok Ped at Phangan.

316
00:27:49,653 --> 00:27:50,921
Not far from Phuket.

317
00:27:54,525 --> 00:27:58,762
The kids can go do acitivites as well. Get some nice photos...

318
00:28:01,165 --> 00:28:04,134
There's tens of places, prices aren't high either

319
00:28:09,540 --> 00:28:10,741
Oh, Tao Sor!

320
00:28:11,108 --> 00:28:11,742
Right on time!

321
00:28:12,176 --> 00:28:15,045
Mom and Dad are finding a place to go camping,

322
00:28:15,179 --> 00:28:17,414
so we can do some activities together.

323
00:28:18,115 --> 00:28:19,617
Oh, I'm...

324
00:28:20,117 --> 00:28:21,185
gonna go draw now.

325
00:28:21,552 --> 00:28:25,155
You haven't drawn us in while! Draw one for us, won't you?

326
00:28:25,589 --> 00:28:28,359
If we do that, then he wouldn't be in the picture with us!

327
00:28:28,559 --> 00:28:29,827
Right, we'll do this.

328
00:28:32,096 --> 00:28:34,264
We have to take a selfie.

329
00:28:34,632 --> 00:28:35,432
Come in.

330
00:28:36,200 --> 00:28:38,268
1, 2, 3. Tao Sor, smile!

331
00:28:38,702 --> 00:28:39,903
Smile a little!

332
00:28:41,438 --> 00:28:43,073
Look over to your mom.

333
00:28:43,574 --> 00:28:45,309
Great, another one!

334
00:28:46,744 --> 00:28:49,747
Alright, Mom? Smile a bit more, Mom!

335
00:28:50,614 --> 00:28:53,283
Okay. Like this, son.

336
00:28:53,751 --> 00:28:56,754
So we'll have you in the picture too, isn't that good?

337
00:28:57,921 --> 00:28:58,956
Yes.

338
00:29:02,726 --> 00:29:03,861
Tao Sor...

339
00:29:04,461 --> 00:29:06,063
You can talk to me if there's something.

340
00:29:06,263 --> 00:29:08,032
I love you very much.

341
00:29:09,700 --> 00:29:10,868
Thank you.

342
00:29:37,661 --> 00:29:38,962
What's wrong, Kim?

343
00:29:41,065 --> 00:29:43,200
Nothing. What are you doing?

344
00:29:46,103 --> 00:29:49,106
Today we went to interview the survivors of the accidents.

345
00:29:49,239 --> 00:29:52,376
It's so sad. She was asleep for 3 years,

346
00:29:52,643 --> 00:29:56,380
and once she woke up, she had lost both her husband and her son.

347
00:29:57,147 --> 00:30:00,150
He's probably not even dead, he might have just been lost at sea.

348
00:30:00,984 --> 00:30:04,021
But 3 years without any signs, doesn't that look like he's gone?

349
00:30:04,388 --> 00:30:08,625
I don't know, but I feel like they'e going to meet.

350
00:30:14,264 --> 00:30:17,267
I don't know who I am.

351
00:30:18,602 --> 00:30:21,138
They just took me in...

352
00:30:24,541 --> 00:30:25,342
I don't know...

353
00:30:27,644 --> 00:30:28,979
why I'm even alive.

354
00:30:31,181 --> 00:30:33,617
Sometimes, it could be true.

355
00:30:33,817 --> 00:30:34,985
What's true?

356
00:30:37,221 --> 00:30:40,324
I think, maybe this woman could be Tao Sor's real mother.

357
00:30:40,858 --> 00:30:42,993
Huh? Is that possible?

358
00:30:43,627 --> 00:30:45,395
What kind of coincidence is that?

359
00:30:46,463 --> 00:30:48,031
Nothing is a coincidence.

360
00:30:48,699 --> 00:30:50,934
Yes, I think we have to bring them together first.

361
00:30:51,535 --> 00:30:52,402
Where is she staying?

362
00:30:52,603 --> 00:30:54,338
She's going back tonight.

363
00:30:54,505 --> 00:30:56,540
We just sent her to the airport.

364
00:30:57,007 --> 00:30:58,876
But if we leave now, we might make it.

365
00:30:58,876 --> 00:31:02,312
Then I'll go ahead. Send me her number and details, okay?

366
00:31:02,312 --> 00:31:02,913
Okay!

367
00:31:04,481 --> 00:31:06,316
Can you send him the details?

368
00:31:27,471 --> 00:31:29,139
Tao Sor.

369
00:31:30,507 --> 00:31:32,176
Tao Sor.

370
00:33:25,022 --> 00:33:28,025
Why do you have to go this far?

371
00:33:28,992 --> 00:33:31,228
I'm protecting you.

372
00:33:42,406 --> 00:33:43,473
That's not true.

373
00:33:44,374 --> 00:33:46,176
Both you and Mom know well, don't you?

374
00:33:54,718 --> 00:33:55,285
Tao Sor.
Tao Sor!

375
00:33:56,086 --> 00:33:56,820
Tao Sor!

376
00:35:17,934 --> 00:35:19,069
What's up, Tao Sor?

377
00:35:21,038 --> 00:35:22,305
Kim..

378
00:35:24,041 --> 00:35:25,108
where are you?

379
00:35:26,910 --> 00:35:27,944
Come see me.

380
00:35:29,079 --> 00:35:30,247
Wait, Tao Sor!

381
00:35:31,148 --> 00:35:33,917
Calm down, tell me where you are.

382
00:35:35,152 --> 00:35:37,020
I'm waiting on the bridge.

383
00:35:38,455 --> 00:35:39,856
Okay, alright.

384
00:35:40,424 --> 00:35:41,558
I'll hurry there.

385
00:35:42,059 --> 00:35:43,260
Wait for me, Tao Sor.

386
00:35:43,894 --> 00:35:44,961
Wait for me.

387
00:37:01,271 --> 00:37:01,905
Tao Sor!

388
00:37:03,907 --> 00:37:04,541
Tao Sor!

389
00:37:04,908 --> 00:37:05,942
Tao Sor, are you asleep?

390
00:37:06,243 --> 00:37:06,877
Tao Sor!

391
00:37:07,511 --> 00:37:08,845
You can't go to sleep now, Tao Sor!

392
00:37:09,846 --> 00:37:10,547
Tao Sor, wake up!

393
00:37:11,348 --> 00:37:12,082
Wake up, Tao Sor!

394
00:37:12,616 --> 00:37:13,483
Tao Sor!

395
00:37:25,762 --> 00:37:26,663
Who are you?

396
00:37:27,097 --> 00:37:27,998
And...

397
00:37:30,200 --> 00:37:31,468
who am I?

398
00:37:35,705 --> 00:37:37,407
Damn it, not now!

399
00:37:40,043 --> 00:37:41,077
My name's Kim,

400
00:37:41,278 --> 00:37:42,379
and your name's Tao Sor.

401
00:37:42,846 --> 00:37:44,414
You and I are lovers.

402
00:37:47,350 --> 00:37:47,918
Here...

403
00:37:48,718 --> 00:37:50,387
our memories are in here.

404
00:37:53,456 --> 00:37:54,324
It's like this!

405
00:37:56,626 --> 00:37:57,961
Where is it?

406
00:38:01,665 --> 00:38:02,699
Let's take it like this,

407
00:38:03,500 --> 00:38:04,334
if you don't believe me...

408
00:38:05,101 --> 00:38:06,436
we have matching tattoos.

409
00:38:06,636 --> 00:38:07,904
We're lovers, Tao Sor!

410
00:38:12,108 --> 00:38:13,777
Right now, we have to hurry and see your mom!

411
00:38:15,245 --> 00:38:16,346
There's no time left, Tao Sor!

412
00:38:16,713 --> 00:38:17,547
Come with me!

413
00:38:17,781 --> 00:38:18,515
Trust me!

414
00:38:18,748 --> 00:38:19,516
Let's go, Tao Sor!

415
00:38:27,991 --> 00:38:28,925
Trust me.

416
00:38:29,192 --> 00:38:30,227
Tao Sor!

417
00:38:31,061 --> 00:38:32,095
Tao Sor!

418
00:38:32,896 --> 00:38:35,365
Come with me, come with me!

419
00:38:46,576 --> 00:38:48,778
There's no time left, we have to get to the airport.

420
00:38:49,679 --> 00:38:51,881
Come with me. Trust me, okay?

421
00:39:07,631 --> 00:39:08,698
I'll be the one

422
00:39:09,633 --> 00:39:11,334
that will be your memory for you.

423
00:40:25,141 --> 00:40:26,643
When will you understand?

424
00:40:27,077 --> 00:40:29,946
Every time he finds out the truth, he turns out like this.

425
00:40:30,313 --> 00:40:33,316
You might think I'm selfish for lying to Tao Sor.

426
00:40:33,616 --> 00:40:36,086
But what good comes from him finding out the truth?

427
00:40:36,353 --> 00:40:37,987
I understand everyone's feelings.

428
00:40:38,822 --> 00:40:40,990
How losing someone can hurt so much.

429
00:40:41,591 --> 00:40:44,594
But I've never thought of replacing my brother.

430
00:40:45,895 --> 00:40:47,664
Because in reality,

431
00:40:48,298 --> 00:40:50,467
no one can really replace anyone else.

432
00:40:50,834 --> 00:40:53,837
Please don't! Don't take Tao Sor away from me!

433
00:40:53,937 --> 00:40:55,071
A person like you...

434
00:40:55,672 --> 00:40:57,440
believes in Holy Power too?

435
00:40:57,707 --> 00:40:59,075
I won't ask you for anything.

436
00:41:02,045 --> 00:41:04,614
But there's something I want to ask from you.

437
00:41:10,320 --> 00:41:12,188
In a few days, I'll be going back to Bangkok.

438
00:41:13,590 --> 00:41:16,559
I want Tao Sor's cooking for my last meal here.

